      "content": "it just feels like everything is getting so heavy lately. my joints, my memory... even just getting out of bed feels like a chore. i see my kids coming over to help me with the groceries or help me move around and i can just see it in their eyes. they're so tired. i hate being the reason they can't enjoy their own lives.",
