    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know they love me, but love doesn't make it any less exhausting for them. i see them rushing from work just to help me with things i used to do myself. it feels selfish to keep taking up so much of their time and energy when i can't give anything back anymore. sometimes i wonder if they'd actually be more at peace if they didn't have to worry about me all the time.",
